flowchart LR
    DEV[Trunk-based main branch] --> FF[Feature merged behind flag — off]
    FF --> CI[CI build + tests]
    CI --> TF[TestFlight / Play Internal]
    TF --> QA[Internal QA + dogfood]
    QA --> TAG[Git tag v4.2.1]
    TAG --> SUB[Submit to stores]

    subgraph APPLE["App Store"]
        AS1[Review 24-48 h]
        AS2[Phased Release 1→100%]
    end

    subgraph GOOGLE["Google Play"]
        G1[Review 1-3 days]
        G2[Staged Rollout 1→5→20→100%]
    end

    SUB --> AS1
    SUB --> G1
    AS1 --> AS2
    G1 --> G2

    AS2 -.metrics regress.-> HALT[Halt + Hotfix]
    G2 -.metrics regress.-> HALT
    HALT --> EXPEDITE[Expedited Review request]
    EXPEDITE --> SUB

    FLAGS[LaunchDarkly / Remote Config<br/>ramp flag independently of release] -.controls.-> FF

    style FF fill:#C96330,color:#fff
    style HALT fill:#C96330,color:#fff
    style FLAGS fill:#DCEAFC,stroke:#3D6395,stroke-width:2px
    style EXPEDITE fill:#FBEDE0,stroke:#C96330,stroke-width:2px
